{"tid":317580,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[以正視聽]今年同往後5年既考生其實好細競爭","createTime":"2017-07-11T14:11:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T08:11:57.000Z","uid":122709,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf16d5279fa7ea48a16d8e3c2f40c069ee722dd6","tid":317580,"uid":122709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:11:00.000Z","msg":"睇返紀錄香港既出生人口由80至到90年代中一直維持大約7萬人<br />\n每年考生人數(日校考生+自修生) 一直都有7萬左右, 而UGC學位只有不足1.5萬<br />\n令到入U率維持係20%左右<br />\n<br />\n但係因為1997年香港主權移交之後,出生率持續低迷,直至05,06年先回升<br />\n1998-2004年既出生人數只有4-5萬, 入U率亦上升至33%以上<br />\n接下來數年直頭有機會<span style=\"color: red;\">16~18分已經有UGC OFFER</span><br />\n<br />\n睇返JUPAS既報名人數,大家都可以明顯咁見到個趨勢<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/uWR6w4Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FuWR6w4Z.png&h=47bd01c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再睇埋出生人口,可以明顯見到98-04年出生人數比較低<br />\n而06年開始可能受到雙非/大量新移民既影響, 慢慢回升<br />\n<br />\n出生年份\t全年出生人數<br />\n<br />\n2015        59,878\t<br />\n2014        62,305\t<br />\n2013        57,084\t<br />\n2012        91,558\t<br />\n2011        95,451\t<br />\n2010        88,584\t<br />\n2009        82,095\t<br />\n2008        78,822\t<br />\n2007        70,875\t<br />\n2006        65,626\t<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2005        57,098</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2004        49,796</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2003        46,965</span>\t<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2002        48,209</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2001        48,219</span>\t<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2000        54,134</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1999        51,281</span>(應屆DSE)\t<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1998        52,977</span><br />\n1997        59,250\t<br />\n1996        63,291\t<br />\n1995        68,637<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/220359_51b0628528f653204bd44f44536c8011.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F220359_51b0628528f653204bd44f44536c8011.png&h=5624dd04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望98-05出世既你地好好珍惜自己既機會, 你地既對手已經相對少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nreferences: <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jupas.edu.hk/tc/statistics/jupas-application-statistics/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jupas.edu.hk%2Ftc%2Fstatistics%2Fjupas-application-statistics%2F&d=%2FhjR98DzZoySTOy%2BaJeKkdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=aaa8ce12\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jupas.edu.hk/tc/statistics/jupas-application-statistics/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://goodpama.com/%E5%87%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%8E%87/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoodpama.com%2F%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%258E%2587%2F&d=%2FhjR98DzZoySTOy%2BaJeKkdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=856d279e\" target=\"_blank\">https://goodpama.com/%E5%87%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%8E%87/</a><br />\n政府統計處資料<a href=\"http://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/B71312FA2013XXXXB0100.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.statistics.gov.hk%2Fpub%2FB71312FA2013XXXXB0100.pdf&d=%2FhjR98DzZoySTOy%2BaJeKkdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=4652b9a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/B71312FA2013XXXXB0100.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"310939b498b04530cacfc6fa71454ffe0f140be8","tid":317580,"uid":47645,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:14:58.000Z","msg":"DLLM之後9萬幾個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab03887525d990155be15a88055645347ceb584","tid":317580,"uid":64582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:20:10.000Z","msg":"黎緊5萬考生都唔夠根本派街坊咁制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd8a980bdebb1b502b79ff4c5e47763cf9f5941","tid":317580,"uid":47645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:21:10.000Z","msg":"回返個正經D 咁有冇check埋按年幾多%係單非雙非 ?"},{"pid":"1413c56c3cad6469c4557ed97fa3f9ce5bdddba5","tid":317580,"uid":31559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:21:33.000Z","msg":"點解我唔係03年出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c82ac3cf8d9911df420c20410f5a4ab02ce786e","tid":317580,"uid":47645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:22:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎緊5萬考生都唔夠根本派街坊咁制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以計下11年出世同03出世個難度系數差幾遠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f82a622e1228eb7268013744e61243acac8417d","tid":317580,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:23:58.000Z","msg":"2012 發生左咩事"},{"pid":"c8c2edab56dbe89990db592c8eea150aaf56a4f1","tid":317580,"uid":90561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:24:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2012 發生左咩事</blockquote><br />\n禁雙非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f493bf7cc36f3e073fa44bacc53ed1037399de5e","tid":317580,"uid":31559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:27:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黎緊5萬考生都唔夠根本派街坊咁制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以計下11年出世同03出世個難度系數差幾遠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n15000個ugc位,假設考生人數=出生人數<br />\n03年 入u率 31.9%<br />\n11年 入u率 15.7%<br />\n仲未計11年自修生人數會多好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6576c466d616465be8fceeafcc7a638524f9aacd","tid":317580,"uid":6132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:31:48.000Z","msg":"預計2023之後入大學難度直線上升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能25分先有u讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b332ef29bed1370b1971867fe1f7d482551030e3","tid":317580,"uid":47645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:33:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>預計2023之後入大學難度直線上升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能25分先有u讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來之後跌返去正常 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a827211d1690a92937e0ee7c46d47dc9c68722b1","tid":317580,"uid":47645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/223347_27d52b42928254d314548c8879a3f0a0.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F223347_27d52b42928254d314548c8879a3f0a0.PNG&h=842f7520&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71079e9b21c32712bf46886ee5528e4b57d7fd1b","tid":317580,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:35:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2012 發生左咩事</blockquote><br />\n禁雙非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85da7926171b8b5a21da2be6129cdc1212e46539","tid":317580,"uid":69037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:36:16.000Z","msg":"咁又唔洗咁驚嘅<br />\n有一半雙非<br />\n佢地讀個d中學通常廢"},{"pid":"48e6c8f713275ddfa41e7a1698dcf1ca506d27c2","tid":317580,"uid":31559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:37:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/223347_27d52b42928254d314548c8879a3f0a0.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F223347_27d52b42928254d314548c8879a3f0a0.PNG&h=842f7520&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來06-12係因為雙非單非搞到咁多人係香港出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搶資源,搶學位"},{"pid":"fff7e18624dd8d7005ec17b80fc5e112991c3444","tid":317580,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:37:45.000Z","msg":"過兩年應該去玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b866a7f243ab9a55509b9e738c399bb76b1d05","tid":317580,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:38:01.000Z","msg":"2012 91,558<br />\n2011 95,451<br />\n2010 88,584<br />\n2009 82,095 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nrip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34baa479b81a310d2e7484d6e9b981350a63d8b7","tid":317580,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:40:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2012 91,558<br />\n2011 95,451<br />\n2010 88,584<br />\n2009 82,095 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nrip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n9萬幾大概都係以前考ce既人數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔算太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04e4a69daf8fcabbd6de0897ac0ad039b294aa1","tid":317580,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:40:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2012 91,558<br />\n2011 95,451<br />\n2010 88,584<br />\n2009 82,095 <br />\n<br />\n<br /